00:42:13.989 --> 00:42:16.989
For example, having period correct materials

00:42:16.989 --> 00:42:20.989
for the temple, as well as accurate stone reliefs.

00:42:20.989 --> 00:42:22.989
After filming was complete,

00:42:22.989 --> 00:42:24.989
the research team noted some scenes

00:42:24.989 --> 00:42:26.989
in the treasury were accidentally shot

00:42:26.989 --> 00:42:28.989
