00:42:34.369 --> 00:42:36.369
additional digital treasures

00:42:36.369 --> 00:42:38.369
and placing them in the foreground.

00:42:38.369 --> 00:42:44.059
As we didn't have the luxury of 185,000 extras,

00:42:44.059 --> 00:42:46.059
actors were dressed in ancient costumes

00:42:46.059 --> 00:42:48.059
and their pictures taken.

00:42:48.059 --> 00:42:52.059
We then used these pictures to create digital extras,

00:42:52.059 --> 00:42:54.059
using crowd-simulating software

00:42:54.059 --> 00:42:57.059
to place them in the scenes and drive their movements.

00:43:00.340 --> 00:43:03.340
